org.paukov.combinatorics.CombinatoricsVector

Packages that use CombinatoricsVector
org.paukov.combinatorics This package contains various stuff to resolve different issues connected to org.paukov.combinatorics such as generating combinatorial objects and etc. 
org.paukov.combinatorics.combination.simple This package generates simple combinations. 
org.paukov.combinatorics.composition This package generates composition of an integer value N. 
org.paukov.combinatorics.partition This package generates partitions. 
org.paukov.combinatorics.permutations This package generates permutations (with and without repetitions). 
org.paukov.combinatorics.subsets This package generates all sunsets of specified set.
